        </a>
      </h1>

    <div class="post-content">
    <p>Andrew and Adam talk with <a href="https://twitter.com/JohnONolan" onclick="javascript:_gaq.push(['_trackEvent','outbound-article','http://twitter.com']);">John O&#8217;Nolan</a> about his open source blogging platform <a href="http://ghost.org/" onclick="javascript:_gaq.push(['_trackEvent','outbound-article','http://ghost.org']);">Ghost</a> written in JavaScript (Node.js), and how he and his team are working hard to create this beautifully designed platform dedicated to one thing: Publishing.</p>

<audio src="http://d.5by5.net/redirect.mp3/fly.5by5.tv/audio/broadcasts/changelog/2013/changelog-105.mp3" controls="controls" preload="none"></audio>

